# Environment Variables for Render.com Deployment

## Backend Service (aws-iam-assessment-api)

Required environment variables:

AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your_access_key_id
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your_secret_access_key
AWS_REGION=us-east-1
PYTHON_VERSION=3.10.0
PORT=10000

## Frontend Service (aws-iam-assessment-ui)

Required environment variables:

VITE_API_URL=https://aws-iam-assessment-api.onrender.com  # Update with your actual backend URL

## How to Set Up in Render Dashboard

1. Navigate to the Environment tab in your service settings
2. Add each variable individually
3. Mark AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID and AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY as secret
4. Save your changes